resources.string: KedditBySteps\nA small Reddit Android client developed using Kotlin

CoordinatorExamples\nThis repository host the source code shown in examples in the article [Mastering Coordinator Layout], there you can find different usages of the CoordinatorLayout, like anchoring views, flexible spaces, swipe to dismiss among other useful tips.
Alerter\nThis library aims to overcome the limitations of Toasts and Snackbars, while reducing the complexity of your layouts.
